{"tid":298711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】食放題好飽 但係仲有二十幾舊壽司","createTime":"2017-06-26T13:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T14:41:06.000Z","uid":63394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"602e61b9da71322aa29612a83e0830096ee38d6b","tid":298711,"uid":63394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"小弟抵死<br />\n頭先同女友食放題<br />\n佢問我要幾多件 三文魚 蝦 咩魚咩魚<br />\n我以為佢問緊魚生，就好爽快咁話6件囉4件囉！<br />\n點知黎到時先發現係壽司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/210202_070604bc8eed5eec669e33d4414903f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F210202_070604bc8eed5eec669e33d4414903f9.jpg&h=9b0ac57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家點算好 <br />\n大家有冇咩方法可以處理到佢地之餘<br />\n又唔會好7"},{"pid":"8378b8e716d733c357b54ec99b34b3b8f3ec4812","tid":298711,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"你d野咁撚難食，點食得落呀，收返佢啦，唔該！"},{"pid":"bf43a2fe352c9c43fbd764ea6e15c8a948fe6370","tid":298711,"uid":63394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你d野咁撚難食，點食得落呀，收返佢啦，唔該！</blockquote><br />\n佢地好似西緊我地面<br />\n唔敢唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e5902a25a641911c3c416086d01c00dae363a9","tid":298711,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"我通常同男朋友猜包剪揼 輸左食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9300d0c37f84de1bd551c4d86f9fe8139012a30c","tid":298711,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"唔柒地話請隔離枱食"},{"pid":"d3ade165e80a0ec9579ae9c06028604afc375ba4","tid":298711,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"剩番咁少就自己食埋啦"},{"pid":"eb7af47056e19